title: Recap: Tech falls twice to #17 Texas Saturday - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech falls twice to #17 Texas Saturday - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – Texas Tech (22-26, 5-13) dropped both games of a doubleheader Saturday against No. 17 Texas (35-15-1, 10-5) as the Longhorns swept the Red Raiders in their Big 12 series finale.
